{"tid":2222461,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"RTX 3080 / 3090 回收謠言終結　NVIDIA 推出驅動程式 456.55 解決","createTime":"2020-09-29T06:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T06:44:57.000Z","uid":120575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b0cb541b9599097e029551d040f4c31afeb9b0","tid":2222461,"uid":120575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:01:32.000Z","msg":"近日有電腦顯示卡 NVIDIA GeForce 3080 的用戶報告指在遊玩電腦遊戲時，會因處理崩潰而令遊戲程式結束，並彈回桌面。早前有德國網媒推測原因是有部份品牌的顯示卡使用的電容有關。而網上更有謠傳指將會回收市面上的RTX 30系列顯示卡。NVIDIA 在昨晚（28日）推出最新驅動程式 456.55，官方指可改善 RTX 30 系列顯示卡的穩定性，用戶可馬上安裝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/09/29/nvidia-rtx-3080-3090/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F09%2F29%2Fnvidia-rtx-3080-3090%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=56ed04df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/09/29/nvidia-rtx-3080-3090/game-channel/</a><br />\n<br />\n之前個Facebook page會唔會比人告？"},{"pid":"3af10da86edc0a98e7beb3d4972f4584b9932cb0","tid":2222461,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:42:14.000Z","msg":"但係個driver係限制OC<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b045e82cb598fd3b67b528a40ee5c8331390850","tid":2222461,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3af10da86edc0a98e7beb3d4972f4584b9932cb0","tid":2222461,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:42:14.000Z","msg":"但係個driver係限制OC<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"封曬一眾OC version<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}